OL,3,CStreet sign made famous by Sir Paul
OL,4,CMcCartney goes missing
OL,6,FA road sign made famous by Sir Paul
OL,7,FMcCartney's latest album has vanished
OL,8,Fjust days after the record's release.
OL,10,FThe street sign for Dungeon Lane,
OL,11,Flocated near Liverpool John Lennon
OL,12,FAirport in Speke, was only reinstalled
OL,13,Fin early May after a surge in Beatles
OL,14,Ftourists. But now an empty metal frame
OL,15,Fis all that remains.
OL,17,FThe location is significant to Sir
OL,18,FPaul who chose an image of the sign
OL,19,Ffor the cover of his 20th studio
OL,20,Falbum, The Boys of Dungeon Lane, which
OL,21,Flaunched on 29 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
