FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780665075
OL,3,CStreet sign made famous by Sir Paul
OL,4,CMcCartney goes missing
OL,6,F"The Boys of Dungeon Lane is out, and
OL,7,Fearly on in the campaign someone
OL,8,Fnicked the sign from Dungeon Lane in
OL,9,FLiverpool. I have no idea who it was,
OL,10,Fbut I've got my suspicions", he said.
OL,12,FThe council restored the signage
OL,13,Ffollowing requests from local tour
OL,14,Fguides, as fans began flocking to the
OL,15,Fsite close to one of McCartney's
OL,16,Fchildhood homes.
OL,18,FMerseyside Police understand the sign
OL,19,Fhas not yet been officially reported
OL,20,Fstolen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780665075
OL,3,CStreet sign made famous by Sir Paul
OL,4,CMcCartney goes missing
OL,6,FHowever, Liverpool City Council
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "It's deeply
OL,8,Fdisappointing to see that someone has
OL,9,Facted selfishly by stealing the sign
OL,10,Ffor Dungeon Lane.
OL,12,F"These signs are an important part of
OL,13,Four streets and reinstalling them
OL,14,Fcosts both taxpayers' money and staff
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,F"With the release of Paul McCartney's
OL,18,Fnew album, we knew that the signage
OL,19,Fwould be popular, and we would expect
OL,20,Fvisitors to show it the proper respect.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
