PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780665075
OL,3,CStreet sign made famous by Sir Paul
OL,4,CMcCartney goes missing
OL,6,F"When the sign is replaced, we ask
OL,7,Fpeople to think of others and to take
OL,8,Fonly photos."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
